These vaccination campaigns are very ambitious but prudent, given the continuation of cases and evidence of circulation of the virus in the sylvan (forest) cycle of transmission. One hopes that they will do follow-up studies on persistence of immunity following vaccination and track any adverse reactions to the vaccine. - Mod.TY]
